Our Story

More Than Coffee.
A State of Mind.

Bunny Beans was born from a single obsession: the pursuit of the perfect cup. Nestled in the heart of the city, our café is a sanctuary for those who believe coffee is not just a drink — it's a ritual, a moment of pause, a small luxury in the rush of everyday life.

We source our beans directly from small-scale, ethically managed farms across Ethiopia, Colombia, and Guatemala. Every roast is crafted in-house, ensuring that each sip carries the full depth of its origin.
